      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient ${\\cal E} : \\frac {x^2}{4a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{4b^2} = 1$,\net ${\\cal E}' : \\frac {x^2}{a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{b^2} = 1$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E} : \\frac {x^2}{4a^2} +\n\\frac {y^2}{4b^2} = 1\\)</span>, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal\nE}&#39; : \\frac {x^2}{a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{b^2} = 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
